title: Dark Secrets: Inside Bohemian Grove (2000) -- High Quality
description:
Since 1873, the global Elite has held secret meetings inside the Bohemian Grove.

Members of this so called "Bohemian Club" includes former Presidents such 
as Eisenhower, Nixon, and Reagan. The Bush Family is also heavily involved.

Each year at the Bohemian Grove, members dress up in robes, and conduct occult rituals, where they worship a giant stone owl they call "Great Owl of Bohemia", 
to which they burn a human, in effigy, as a sacrifice...


In this documentary, you will see the infiltration of the Grove, 
and also see the ritual itself, called "The Cremation of Care".
